\begin_inset Formula $c\bar{c}$
\end_inset

 pair.
 Thus, if we want to define an 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

inclusive
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{2}^{c}$
\end_inset

, it seems we must include those cases where the charm in contained in the
